ATTRIBUTE-SET - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-mpls-te-oper:mpls-te-standby/p2p-p2mp-tunnel/tunnel-heads/tunnel-head/{tunnel-name}/destination/path-option/attribute-set/

Retrieve operation of resource: attribute-set

tunnel-name: string
in path

ID of tunnel-name

200 OK
attribute-set_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

ATTRIBUTE-SET-UNION - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-mpls-te-oper:mpls-te-standby/p2p-p2mp-tunnel/tunnel-heads/tunnel-head/{tunnel-name}/destination/path-option/attribute-set/attribute-set-union/

Retrieve operation of resource: attribute-set-union

tunnel-name: string
in path

ID of tunnel-name

200 OK
attribute-set-union_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

ATTRIBUTE-SET-UNION - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-mpls-te-oper:mpls-te-standby/p2p-p2mp-tunnel/tunnel-heads/tunnel-head/{tunnel-name}/destination/path-option/xro-attribute-set/attribute-set-union/

Retrieve operation of resource: attribute-set-union

tunnel-name: string
in path

ID of tunnel-name

200 OK
attribute-set-union_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

AUTOROUTE-ANNOUNCE-TABLE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-mpls-te-oper:mpls-te-standby/announce-tunnels-info/autoroute-announce-table/

Retrieve operation of resource: autoroute-announce-table

200 OK
autoroute-announce-table_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
